        <mxCell id="FMh0UY3MeKUiwhmyRA-H-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;Ticket Booking Application&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="80" width="160" x="250" y="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="FMh0UY3MeKUiwhmyRA-H-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=13;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Functional Requirement&amp;nbsp;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="170" x="55" y="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="FMh0UY3MeKUiwhmyRA-H-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=13;" value="&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ouebg&quot; data-start=&quot;149&quot; data-end=&quot;273&quot;&gt;The system must allow users to search and discover events using filters such as event title, location (city), and date.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1xwy2ga&quot; data-start=&quot;275&quot; data-end=&quot;383&quot;&gt;The system must display detailed event information including seat availability (available vs occupied).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;szaiz5&quot; data-start=&quot;385&quot; data-end=&quot;499&quot;&gt;The system must provide additional event metadata such as description, cast, duration, language, and ratings.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1tybvj8&quot; data-start=&quot;501&quot; data-end=&quot;581&quot;&gt;The system must allow users to select specific seats from a seating layout.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1wiw2d&quot; data-start=&quot;583&quot; data-end=&quot;691&quot;&gt;The system must enable users to securely complete ticket booking transactions and receive confirmation.&lt;/li&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="510" x="70" y="230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="FMh0UY3MeKUiwhmyRA-H-5" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=13;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Non-Functional Requirement&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="210" x="45" y="350" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="FMh0UY3MeKUiwhmyRA-H-6" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=13;" value="&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The system must support scalability to handle up to 100 million daily active users (DAU).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The system must ensure high availability for search and event viewing, even under heavy traffic.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The system should tolerate slight data staleness (event listings, seat counts) instead of system downtime.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The system must ensure strong consistency during seat booking to prevent double booking.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The system must provide low latency responses for search, viewing, and booking operations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;735&quot; data-end=&quot;1237&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="140" width="540" x="28" y="410" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="FMh0UY3MeKUiwhmyRA-H-7" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=13;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;API Design&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="90" x="60" y="550" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="FMh0UY3MeKUiwhmyRA-H-8" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=13;" value="&lt;ol data-start=&quot;228&quot; data-end=&quot;1348&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1qeyqs4&quot; data-start=&quot;228&quot; data-end=&quot;439&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;231&quot; data-end=&quot;254&quot;&gt;Authentication APIs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;260&quot; data-end=&quot;439&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1raae2u&quot; data-start=&quot;260&quot; data-end=&quot;312&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;262&quot; data-end=&quot;288&quot;&gt;POST /api/v1/auth/signup&lt;/code&gt; → Register a new user&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;icbf4g&quot; data-start=&quot;316&quot; data-end=&quot;382&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;318&quot; data-end=&quot;343&quot;&gt;POST /api/v1/auth/login&lt;/code&gt; → Authenticate user and return token&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;q50f0&quot; data-start=&quot;386&quot; data-end=&quot;439&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;388&quot; data-end=&quot;410&quot;&gt;GET /api/v1/users/me&lt;/code&gt; → Get current user profile&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Event Management APIs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;262&quot; data-end=&quot;288&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;262&quot; data-end=&quot;288&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;POST /api/v1/auth/signup&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;→ Register a new user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;318&quot; data-end=&quot;343&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;POST /api/v1/auth/login&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;→ Authenticate user and return token&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;388&quot; data-end=&quot;410&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;GET /api/v1/users/me&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;→ Get current user profile&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/code&gt;" vertex="1">
